context:
KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;밧줄은 퀴케그의 어마어마한 악력으로, 그리고 자신만이 아는 방식으로 직접 꼬았었기에…&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;It is said that Queequeg's ropes, twisted by her powerful grip and her esoteric techniques…&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt; 세상의 그 어떤 매듭보다 질기고 억세다고 한다.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;... are tougher than any other rope in the world.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;그리고 퀴케그는 자신을 호수 속에 혼자 두지 말라고 했다.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;Queequeg told me to not leave her alone in the cold, dark Lake.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;송장인 채로 가라앉아서 고래와 인어들에게 뜯어 먹히고 싶지는 않다고.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;That she didn't want the Whales and Mermaids to tear her apart&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;and devour her when her corpse sinks deep into its waters.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;그건 나도 마찬가지였다.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;I agreed.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;나만이 알고 있는 그 온 살갗의 상처들을, 파헤쳐진 흔적들을… 고작 그것들이 파먹도록 두고 싶지는 않았다.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;The wounds on her skin that only I knew of... the memories of her pain...&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;I didn't want those monsters to heartlessly rip into them, to gorge themselves with her scarred flesh.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;그래서 퀴케그는 관을 만들었다.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;So, Queequeg built herself a coffin.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;밧줄을 있는 힘껏 묶어서 배가 아무리 휘청거려도 자기가 잠든 관만큼은 가라앉지 않도록.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;Built hardily and fastened with ropes twisted and knotted with all her strength.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;So that her coffin would not sink no matter how precariously the ship swayed.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#63a130&gt;내 배에 올라타라, 그리고 호수 밑바닥 끝까지 가는 거다.&lt;/color=#63a130&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#63a130&gt;Come aboard my ship. And sail with me to the cold abyss of the Lake.&lt;/color=#63a130&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;나는 앞으로 불행할 때나 행복할 때나…&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;In joy, and in sorrow... I'll never forget...&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;내게서부터 뜯겨 나간 그 끈들을 기억하겠지.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;... the strands that were ripped away from me.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;이 호수에 영영 갇혀버린 채로 평생을 잠겨 있겠지.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;I'll be buried in this Lake forever to my last gasping breath.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;차오르는 물을 벗어나려고 해도 호흡에 들어오는 건 고독뿐.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ff9500&gt;Try as I might to escape the rising waters, only loneliness fills my lungs.&lt;/color=#ff9500&gt;
